name: rev-cow-graphos
description:
It was made with 31 curated photos of white women having sex with men, reverse cowgirl style. Trained on URPM.

A big shout-out and thanks to Holostrawberry for his Lora guide and help.

If you like my work and want more quality Loras, you can buy me a large coffee :-) here: https://ko-fi.com/graphos888

I recommend a weight of: 0.7 - 0.9, depending on the model you are working with.

Triggerword: rev-cow-graphos

Size 768x512 or 512x768. + Turn off "restore faces" and instead do Hires. fix, use 4x-UltraSharp / R-ESRAGAN 4x+, Denoising strength 0.35.

I recommend this kind of prompt:

rev-cow-graphos,photograph of a (subject) sitting on a man getting fucked in (anal/vagina), reverse cowgirl position,(settings/where is it)<lora:rev-cow-graphos-v2:0.65>

Negative prompt:

Cow,(deformed iris, deformed pupils, semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, anime, mutated hands and fingers:1.4), (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, amputation, child, childish


Hope you like it, and I can´t wait to see what you can create with it.

Please, give it a good review if you like it.

Thanks.
